Devel-Gladiator version 0.04
===============================

Devel::Gladiator iterate's Perl's internal memory structures and can be used
to enumerate all the currently live SVs.

This can be used to hunt leaks and to profile memory usage.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

